Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.app

Contains replacement response, command extension and response extension classes for the Domain Name Application extension.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DomainCreateApplicationCommandExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Create command, representing the Create Application and Allocate Application aspects of the Domain Name Application extension.
DomainCreateApplicationResponseExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Create response, representing the Application Create aspect of the Domain Name Application extension.
DomainDeleteApplicationCommandExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Delete command, representing the Delete Application aspect of the Domain Name Application extension.
DomainInfoApplicationCommandExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Info command, representing the Application Info aspect of the Domain Name Application extension.
DomainInfoApplicationResponseExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Info response, representing the Application Info aspect of the Domain Name Application extension.
DomainUpdateApplicationCommandExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Update command, representing the Update Application aspect of the Domain Name Application extension.

Contains replacement response, command extension and response extension classes for the Domain Name Application extension.
